plugins.description:
Generate a palette of colors using CSS variables.

input:

/* bluegray-palette */
$bluegrey-50: #ECEFF1;
$bluegrey-200: #B0BEC5;
$bluegrey-400: #78909C;
$bluegrey-600: #546E7A;
$bluegrey-800: #37474F;

output:

A new framed collection of named rectangles matching the colors in your input.

